{"tid":1120943,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]《聖鬥士星矢覺醒》(22) 屌你老母刷極都無匙","createTime":"2019-04-23T04:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T08:43:02.000Z","uid":9526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4adb1a94ed85d3656a1265044c685c8a9f63e101","tid":1120943,"uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZZy9SRHQQsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZZy9SRHQQsc&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e4680128\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZZy9SRHQQsc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajnCOvv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajnCOvv.jpg&h=783ed862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/rWV1vJ1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWV1vJ1.jpg&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=10b92f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/rWV1vJ1.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]忘記領取月禮包魔法石和抽卡 請問有什麼補救辦法嗎靈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBH3J4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBH3J4z.jpg&h=3e1e706e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DSGvQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DSGvQ0.jpg&h=d4bb37e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBnGvRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBnGvRi.jpg&h=6753b8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfzxCwk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbfzxCwk.jpg&h=70498eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n26號中午12點開服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://sds.gamamobi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsds.gamamobi.com&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=879b6804\" target=\"_blank\">https://sds.gamamobi.com</a><br />\nfacebook:<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sds.Seiya/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsds.Seiya%2F&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e07421dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sds.Seiya/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲介紹</span></span><br />\n隻GAME玩乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻GAME類似陰陽師嘅玩法，收集唔同<del>性</del>聖鬥士<br />\n以6個角色組成一隊，角色出招要用到能量(熟陰陽師嘅可以當佢係火)<br />\n而且可以跨服同其他玩家協力打關，講求合作性同配隊<br />\n玩咩SER好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸GAME手法不嬲興開十九幾個SER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以如果驚追唔上班大課長可以揀比較新嘅SER玩，想抱大腿嘅可以揀SER1(目前比較多巴打玩嘅SER)<br />\n<br />\nSER1軍團 LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n加左後麻煩係POST/GAME到PM番團長/副團長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首抽攻略</span></span> <br />\n快刷首抽，一場都唔駛打，之前冇野送就大約1分鐘一次，宜家係唔係有禮物石可以刷多幾下？<br />\n1）開新ac或新set = 50石<br />\n2）抽邪武，右下角分享拎30石（好友分享就得）= 80石<br />\n3）之後佢叫你按劇情，你唔好按劇情個位，是但喺空白位按幾下，佢會問你係咪跳過，揀是<br />\n4）按左上角星矢圖像，擴展下載。拎多20石 = 100石<br />\n*宜家新ac好似有獎勵，總共會有300幾石可以抽3下<br />\n抽野，中就開唔中就切換帳號由頭嚟過<br />\n=========<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">首抽建議</span></span><br />\n1.雙子座撒卡<br />\n目前全GAME最高群體傷兼無視敵方念防(魔防)，培養難度低，新手抽中佢一開始可以無腦過關<br />\n2.雙魚座阿布羅狄<br />\n輸出系，只要留能量比佢到最後可以一波打死人，傷害唔講得少<br />\n3.天蠍座米羅<br />\n同樣係輸出系，優勝之處係唔需要用到能量去出技而且主要輸出係1技，運用方法係出2技＞1技去做輸出，配合B級角六分儀可以即時做出一套連技，不過好食技書去升技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />課長可以無視以上嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.白羊座穆<br />\n全GAME最勁嘅神坦，可以幫自己/隊友開盾而且仲會吸收盾所受到嘅傷害再用3技出真傷還番比人，反擊流必要隊員之一<br />\n5.水瓶座卡妙<br />\n冰隊核心隊員，配合冰河可以成為現時最流行嘅冰隊，2技可以冰人一回合，3技因應對面疊加嘅印記而提高傷害<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剛開始國服抽卡不給碎片，但現在改限時抽卡活動會有碎片給，變相保底但還是得抽夠一定次數的量，神沙屬於特典活動，國服活動結束不入一般卡池，有能力務必抽到，有些卡是必要的，就像有神沙跟沒神沙是兩個遊戲，刚开服其实不用特别去抽那个S卡，存星石等候面卡出来在抽，脸好会附带不少S出现。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">by結蕉渠蓋龜苓膏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n實用A卡<br />\n珍妮，水蛇，仙王，魔鈴，蜥蝪，楓，六怪獸，火鳥，一輝，逆鳞紫龍<br />\n<br />\n實用B卡<br />\n星矢，偷火狗，小熊，黑暗祭司，六分儀，卡西歐士，貴鬼<br />\n白鯨，巴比倫，大熊<br />\n<br />\nPVE(優先)<br />\n珍妮，仙王，魔鈴，六怪獸，六魔獸，六分儀，貴鬼，星矢，黑暗祭司<br />\n<br />\nPVP自行配搭<br />\n<br />\n首抽建議(25/3/2019)<br />\n童虎，射手，撒加，雙魚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">小字宙</span></span></span><br />\n小宇宙類似以前魔靈同陰陽師嘅符文同魂咁 都係用黎幫角色提升能力值<br />\n而且會有唔同效果<br />\n以下係轉自巴哈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/205621_1bf998eb165c2403c14e51664ea4bcfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F205621_1bf998eb165c2403c14e51664ea4bcfa.png&h=1a5a38ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/205620_4ac45d411b91c0eea56b606bfcadaa4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F205620_4ac45d411b91c0eea56b606bfcadaa4d.png&h=56658a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥士殿堂升級方法<br />\n商店&rarr;榮譽&rarr;買高級鮮花禮盒<br />\n盡量買<br />\n挑戰幣打鬥士pvp<br />\n榮譽幣打銀河(新手唔夠打都要刷到滿)<br />\n鬥士殿堂3同5階會有效果增加 <br />\n<br />\n抽野傳說及其他攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ruan8.com/gonglue/9742.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ruan8.com%2Fgonglue%2F9742.html&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=26536bc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ruan8.com/gonglue/9742.html</a><br />\n超級實用攻略 轉自巴哈<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33366&amp;snA=78&amp;tnum=95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D33366%26snA%3D78%26tnum%3D95&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5d3bd993\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33366&amp;snA=78&amp;tnum=95</a><br />\n<br />\n陸服角色推出參考<br />\n8月2 開服<br />\n8月24 射手座<br />\n9月21 童虎<br />\n9月25 開海皇篇<br />\n10月1 加隆<br />\n10月26 海王子<br />\n11月23 沙加<br />\n1月1 史昂<br />\n2月1 波塞頓<br />\n2月19 重開沙加<br />\n3月8 潘多拉<br />\n<br />\n1001開POST template<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=47b5f4d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qBKvCTQyJFXGMMZb3Yp3Au5Z8D3wzvcBodJBUaRgpus/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nS1 LIHKG團員LIST 麻煩入左團同想申團嘅係入面加番自己個連登名同Game名<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1lOJgGuX-_RIEDHPDLbdUKpajkYhFiGK6HUCU_6BPPik/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1lOJgGuX-_RIEDHPDLbdUKpajkYhFiGK6HUCU_6BPPik%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=9398c35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1lOJgGuX-_RIEDHPDLbdUKpajkYhFiGK6HUCU_6BPPik/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"4d559fe1206d332c7bbde9fd3ff869acbd2bdc5d","tid":1120943,"uid":13270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"第一次課金android點課最抵？上官網課？定買點卡？"},{"pid":"ba6a1eca0e131533113f209896ea40876d192c0c","tid":1120943,"uid":122750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"神沙, 童虎, 邊隻上6星先好D?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}